Package: yardlistr
Type: Package
Title: Generate Summary Plots from eBird Data
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person(
        given = "Gleb G.",
        family = "Ebert",
        role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
        email = "dev@gl-eb.me",
        comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7734-3824")
    )
  )
Description: The yardlistr package loads your personal eBird data from a csv
    file, processes checklists from a user-specified list of locations and
    generates a variety of plots for each location.
